...that nourishes the lashes while making them naturally fluffy! 

Ad | This is the Badgal Bounce Voluminizing Mascara by @benefitindia . It has a genius custom-engineered wand that coats your lashes with just the right amount of formula, and the fine-tooth comb separates and defines each lash for maximum volume and lift. Plus, it lasts all day (like, 24 hours!) without clumping or flaking. I tried it for a whole 9-to-5 and it didn’t budge. 

And the best part? It’s super nourishing, thanks to ingredients like pro-vitamin B5 and castor seed oil. It’s not too tough to remove either - just a swipe with a nice cleansing balm and you’re sorted!

#makeup #beauty #lashes #eyemakeup #mascara #lashlift #benefitindia #bouncemascara #badgalbounce #benefitcosmetics

Saves 90% of your makeup! 

Never Waste Makeup Again with this beauty blender that mimics your fingerprint! 

If you’re tired of your beauty sponge soaking up more foundation than your face, @realtechniques the Makeup Saver Sponger. is a revolutionary product that deserves a spot in every makeup lover’s kit. I see it living up to the hype! 

This isn’t just another beauty blender knockoff. The Makeup Saver Sponger is engineered with fingerprint mimicking technology, allowing it to blend like your fingers would but with a smoother, more controlled finish. That textured surface isn’t just for show; it grips and moves product like skin on skin contact, giving you precision and seamless coverage.

But the real showstopper? It absorbs 90% less makeup.

We’ve all been personally victimized by sponges that drink up our expensive foundations, but this one’s a total game changer. Thanks to its ultra low absorption design, your makeup ends up where it belongs – on your face. That means more mileage out of every bottle and far less waste.

Whether you’re applying foundation, concealer, or cream blush, the sponge delivers a flawless, airbrushed finish without streaks or cakiness. It’s soft yet firm, easy to clean, and feels luxurious in the hand. The ergonomic shape hugs contours and under eyes effortlessly.

TLDR: This sponge is smart upgrade that saves product, time, and money. If you’re someone who values flawless results and hates wasting makeup, this little innovation is 100% worth the hype.

#beauty #makeup #beautyblender #realtechniques #foundation

Slushy primer that makes your pores disappear?!

The texture is wild. Think soft, squishy slush, almost like chilled jelly. It’s so satisfying to touch and honestly makes applying primer feel way more fun than it should be. This is the @milanicosmetics Conceal + Perfect Blur Out Smoothing Primer.

The second it hits your skin, you get this icy cold sensation, like your face just dipped into a snowbank (but make it skincare). It’s super refreshing, especially in the morning or after a long day.

But here’s the real magic: it blurs pores like a filter. The formula has that smooth, silicone like finish that glides over texture and fine lines, leaving your skin soft, matte, and prepped. Foundation applies like butter on top and stays put.

If you’re into makeup that feels cool (literally) and gives you that soft focus finish without feeling heavy, this one’s a total win.
And that slushy texture? Lowkey addictive.

Let tiny needles prick my face?! Sounds intense, right?

Ad | But @thedermacoindia Retinol Microneedling Serum Shot is way less scary than it sounds and actually kind of amazing. 

The microneedles give a mild, tingly prick (definitely not painful), and they help the retinol sink deeper into your skin for better results. After just a few uses, I noticed smoother texture, a more even tone, and a healthy glow that made me feel like I’d just had a facial. The formula is strong, great for targeting fine lines, dullness, and uneven skin, but beginners should definitely ease in slowly and never skip SPF. The single-use “shots” are super hygienic and mess-free, making the whole routine feel kind of luxe. If you’re looking to seriously level up your skincare and don’t mind a little tingle for big results, this one’s 100 percent worth trying.

#beauty #skincare #microneedling #ad

Glass hair goals? Achieved in just 9 seconds. ✨

Ad | My new shower hair obsession: @raisebeautyindia On Cloud 9 Treatment. This magic-in-a-bottle transforms from ampoule to cream and works better and a lot quicker than most conditioners. If you’ve been sleeping on this, here’s your sign to try it — and you can use FIZA20 for 20% OFF on your order. 💆‍♀️🛁

It’s quick, it’s easy, and it seriously works. Post shampoo, apply it on your damp scalp and hair, massage to transform the ampoule, leave it for 9 seconds and Rinse. It’s that simple!! And The result? A healthier scalp and ridiculously soft, silky and shiny hair 

Raise is also available on Amazon, so go and grab yours now! @bouncebeautyindia 

#ElevateEveryday #beauty #haircare #hair #glasshair #shine

Melt the day away!

Ad | If you wear makeup regularly or live in a city, you know how hard it can be to find a cleansing oil that actually gets everything off without leaving your skin feeling dry or irritated. That’s why I was so pleasantly surprised by Anua’s Heartleaf Pore Control Cleansing Oil. It’s gentle, effective, and just really nice to use.

The texture is super light and silky, and it glides over your skin like a dream. It breaks down sunscreen, foundation, and even waterproof mascara in seconds. No scrubbing needed. And when you rinse it off, it turns into this soft milky texture that washes away clean without any greasy residue.

One of the things I really appreciate is that it doesn’t leave your skin feeling tight or stripped. Just clean, balanced, and soft. It also has heartleaf extract, which is known for calming and soothing the skin, so it’s perfect if you’re sensitive or breakout prone. And there’s no added fragrance or harsh ingredients, which is always a win.

Overall, it’s a solid first step in any cleansing routine and one I actually look forward to using. It makes taking off the day feel like a little self care ritual.

@anua_global #anua #doublecleansing #doublecleanse #anuacleansingoil #cleansingoil #makeupremover #cleansing #ulta #ultaskintok #sephora #skincareroutine #koreanskincare #pore #blackheads

Paint brush eyeshadow = Instant sparkle with zero effort! ✨

If you love a one-step, no-fuss eye look that still turns heads, the @urbandecaycosmetics 24/7 Glaze-On Shimmer Liquid Eyeshadow might just become your new go-to.

This liquid shadow goes on super smooth with a cooling glide that feels kind of amazing. The built-in applicator makes it easy to swipe on in seconds—no brushes, no fallout, no mess. Just dab, blend with a fingertip, and boom: shimmer, depth, and dimension in one go.

The formula has a gorgeous multidimensional shimmer without feeling glittery or over-the-top. It catches the light just enough to make your eyes pop, but still feels wearable for everyday. And once it sets, it’s locked in. No creasing, no smudging, no weird fading halfway through the day. I even wore it through a sweaty concert and it didn’t budge.

The shade I’m wearing is Silver Spooning -  cool-toned silver shimmer.. It’s quick, fun, and makes it look like you tried way harder than you did. 

#beauty #makeup #eyeshadow #eyemakeup

Calligraphy felt tip pen for a lip stain that leaves such a uniform long lasting colour!

The applicator on the @stilacosmetics Calligraphy lip stain literally looks like one of those felt-tip pens, and I have to admit, it makes applying the color super precise. LIt’s great if you’re into that sharp, clean look without needing a separate lip liner.

The color payoff is surprisingly strong for a stain - it goes on rich and smooth, with no patchiness. And once it sets? It’s locked in. No smudging, no transfer, even through eating and drinking.

It dries quickly to a soft matte finish and feels super lightweight, almost like there’s nothing on your lips. Just a heads up: if your lips are dry or chapped, it can cling a little, so exfoliating beforehand helps for any lip stain. 

Overall, this is a killer choice if you’re after long-lasting color with precision and zero fuss throughout the day.

#beauty #makeup #lips #lipstain #stilacosmetics

Foundation suspended in a serum? An affordable dupe for the Chanel Water-Fresh Tint, might I say. 

This @covergirl Simply Ageless Skin Perfector Essence Foundation is honestly such a viral gem. It has those pigment droplets suspended in a serum base. You can literally see the little pigment pearls floating in the bottle, and when you blend it in, they burst and melt right into your skin.

The texture is so lightweight / it feels like skincare going on, not makeup. It gives a soft, dewy finish, but not too shiny or greasy. Just that healthy, fresh-skin look. I love that it evens out my tone and adds a bit of glow without feeling like I have foundation on.

Honestly, for the price and the finish, it’s kind of a no-brainer if you’ve ever looked at the Chanel one and hesitated. This gives such a similar effect for way less.

#beauty #makeup #skin #dupe #chanel #covergirl #foundation

Did that really just happen? 

A solid eye brightener and concealer that doesn’t burn a hole in our pockets! 

The @elfcosmetics putty Color-Correcting eye Brightener is for anyone looking to give their under-eyes a quick refresh without spending a fortune. From the moment you apply it, the creamy texture melts into the skin, leaving a soft, slightly luminous finish. It doesn’t feel heavy or cakey - just light and hydrating. I’ve noticed it works especially well under concealer, acting almost like a smoothing primer that helps everything last longer. If you’re someone who deals with dark circles or just wants to look a little more awake in the morning, this is a really easy step to add into your routine.

Disclaimer: I used an eye shadow in the beginning to enhance my dark circles. There is no gimmick in how the product works. I have NOT used any other concealer, apart from the one shown in the video. No filters used! 

#beauty #makeup #eye #eyemakeup #darkcircles

This is my #1 lip balm – hands down! 
Summer Fridays who? 

And now that it comes in three more shades, I love each one of them. No exaggeration, and no, this IS NOT a paid collaboration. 
#notsponsored 

I genuinely believe that if there’s one lip balm you need to try, it’s this. I know for a fact you’re going to love it, and there’s no going back. Where do I even begin?

@indewild’s original Dewy Lip Treatment (DLT) is a clear balm that delivers intense hydration. Infused with ingredients that mimic desi ghee, it helps repair and soften dry, cracked lips. It’s non-sticky, has a clean scent, and just feels so comforting. I find myself reaching for this constantly. It’s become a staple in my routine, really! 

If you’re into tints, you’ll love the new shades. 
Wedding Rose is a soft, rosy pink that flatters every skin tone and smells faintly of fresh petals. 

Glazed Jalebi brings the fun with its warm, golden shimmer and sweet, caramel-like scent -I only wear it over my lipstick for the glitter. 

And then there’s Caffeine Addict - a rich, mocha-toned brown that gives a sheer wash of color and smells like your favorite cup of coffee. 

All three shades feel just as nourishing as the original, with that same buttery texture and addictive feel.
